Implement a **two-tier progressive search** that returns instant results via Model2Vec (potion-multilingual-128M), then refines rankings in the background using a warm transformer (all-MiniLM-L6-v2) via the daemon.

## Architecture

```
User Query
    │
    ├──→ [potion-multilingual-128M] ──→ Results in ~1ms (display immediately)
    │         (in-process)
    │
    └──→ [all-MiniLM-L6-v2 daemon] ──→ Refined scores in ~130ms
              (warm process)                  │
                                              ▼
                                      Smooth re-rank animation
```

